opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 10th day of September, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Application for Immediate Hearing on the Writ of Habeas Corpus Petition and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
